dcterms:description: The dataset comprises 4000 coding problems with submissions in multiple programming languages. The problem descriptions can be used as a natural language modality, while the code submissions can be used as a programming language modality, forming NL-PL pairs.
dcterms:title: IBM CodeNet dataset
